

Similar to step 2, I recommend making symbolic links for the input and output. 

   $ ln -s /glade/work/lvank/from_cartesius/b.e21.BHIST.f09_g17.CMIP6-historical.003b/DstGrid3d input

and the output files:

   $ mkdir /glade/work/lvank/from_cartesius/b.e21.BHIST.f09_g17.CMIP6-historical.003b/DstGrid2d
   $ ln -s /glade/work/lvank/from_cartesius/b.e21.BHIST.f09_g17.CMIP6-historical.003b/DstGrid2d output

